CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: WhiteHorse Finance Inc is a non-diversified, closed-end management investment company. It makes debt investments in privately held, small-cap companies located in North America. Its investment objective is to generate attractive risk-adjusted returns for investors, primarily by originating senior secured loans to privately held small-cap companies across a broad range of industries.
